openfortivpn
============
A python script for running openfortivpn

# Usage
```
1. cp openfortivpn_runner.py /usr/local/bin/
2. chmod +x /usr/local/bin/openfortivpn_runner.py
3. put your config file in /etc/openfortivpn/
4. edit your crontab:
* * * * *	root	/usr/bin/env python3 /usr/local/bin/openfortivpn_runner.py
```
